OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few showers across eastern
OL,6,Fcoastal parts, but generally a dry
OL,7,Fstart with some good spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine. However the showers develop
OL,9,Fmore widely this morning, becoming
OL,10,Foccasionally heavy with a risk of hail
OL,11,Fand thunder. Occasionally fresh
OL,12,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells and a
OL,15,Ffew showers this evening. Then dry
OL,16,Fovernight with long clear spells
OL,17,Fdeveloping. Touch of frost possible in
OL,18,Fsheltered spots. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
