OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA few east coast showers at
OL,6,Ffirst, otherwise a dry and largely
OL,7,Fsunny start. Some cloud develops for
OL,8,Fthe afternoon but it remains dry.
OL,9,FNorthwesterly breeze continuing to
OL,10,Fease.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells Saturday, some
OL,14,Fevening rain. Overnight rain soon
OL,15,Fclearing Sunday then sunny spells and
OL,16,Fa few showers. Rather cloudy Monday
OL,17,Fwith a little rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
